I was only able to find 75% of the books. If you have any of the three I couldn't find, I would really appreciate you getting it to me (via a comment to this torrent or something). I will be scanning one of the three (Archeofuturism) in september assuming no one else can get me a scan, and will append that scan to this collection then.
